data.description: Prepare to be pleasantly surprised, because this unassuming home is a hidden gem that's about to steal your heart and make you reach for your checkbook!  Stay safe at home with high impact windows and slider.  New roof in 2016, New AC in 2018.  The spacious great room has modern laminate flooring and a new island kitchen with grey shaker style cabinets, soft close doors and drawers, and granite counters that will give you years of enjoyment.  Outside there is a large tiled screened porch, outdoor grill area, large shed for storing all your outside toys/tools, and even a rain water capture system.The fenced yard will give you plenty of space for your little ones or pets to play.  All utility assessments paid.  It's ready for new owners to come and enjoy for years to come.
